&lt;p&gt;As part of the St Andrews Centre for Plastic Surgery, Mayflower Ward is a 12 bedded in patient ward as well an elective and trauma patient assessment ward. The ward are looking for a part time ward clerk/receptionist who will become part of the busy team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience of ward clerking is preferred.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicant&#39;s need to be computer literate and have excellent communication skills. You would need to be able to deal with the general public and have compassion in relation to their admission status.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
